Feature: Login Api Testing

  @Smoke
  Scenario: successful login
    Given: prepare the login request
    When: I send the Login request 
    Then: I should recive 200 as status code
    And: The response should contain login tok

  @negative
  Scenario: Unsuccessful login
    Given: prepare the invalid login request
    When: I send the login request
    Then: I should receive 401 status code
